flowchart LR
    A[Distilled Record Candidate] -->|Pydantic schema validation| B[Typed MemoryRecord]
    B -->|initial status by type| C{Record type}

    C -->|skill/fact/strategy/preference/heuristic| D[status quarantine]
    C -->|failure/trace| E[status active]

    D -->|maintain_memory promote_quarantined after min hours| F[status active]
    E --> F

    F -->|retrieval usage successful| G[reinforce confidence/reuse_count]
    F -->|retrieval usage harmful| H[demote confidence]
    H -->|harmful hits threshold| I[status quarantine]

    F -->|TTL expired| J[status stale]
    J -->|maintenance decay or revive by update| K[may return active]

    F -->|consolidation merge losers| L[status deprecated]

    G --> M[(Backend persisted row)]
    I --> M
    J --> M
    L --> M
